::Banzai-Tron was flying away from the Alliance base.  he knew what he was 
looking for. He neared the coordinates and smiled. This would be fun. He gets 
closer to Airazor and Tigerhawk::
Banzai-Tron: Goodbye, baby!
::He fired all of his weapons at Airazor, who falls to the ground::
Airazor: Unhh, Tigerhawk, hel-
::She was cut off by going into stasis lock::
Banzai-Tron: Oh yeah! Whack for muh daddy-o!
::he looks to Tigerhawk::
Banzai-Tron: Oh, was that your girl? Sorry about that, but if its any 
consolation youre about to be reunited!
::He fires 2 missles at Tigerhawk::
